{"id":1505,"date":"2019-02-18T16:00:12","date_gmt":"2019-02-18T09:00:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=1505"},"modified":"2019-02-18T16:00:12","modified_gmt":"2019-02-18T09:00:12","slug":"thiet-ke-phong-tam-6m2-cuc-xinh-va-tien-nghi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/thiet-ke-phong-tam-6m2-cuc-xinh-va-tien-nghi","title":{"rendered":"Chia s\u1ebb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 c\u1ef1c xinh v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n nghi"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm<\/strong> lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 1 c\u0103n nh\u00e0 ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh. C\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c gia ch\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, ti\u1ec7n nghi&#8230; \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm k\u00edn \u0111\u00e1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft h\u00f4m nay MM2 xin chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c gia ch\u1ee7 <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2<\/strong> c\u1ef1c xinh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec7n nghi. Hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c gia ch\u1ee7 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1506 size-full\" title=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 xinh\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/phong-tam-6-m2-dep.jpg\" alt=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 xinh\" width=\"560\" height=\"387\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi c\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1edf ph\u00eda cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u0103n nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u thang. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u0103n nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea7u thang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Do \u0111\u00f3, hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 \u1edf cu\u1ed1i c\u0103n nh\u00e0.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0&gt;&gt;&gt; N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem: <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong>C\u00e1c l\u01b0u \u00fd khi x\u00e2y nh\u00e0 t\u1eafm k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u thang<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3y g\u1ecdi ngay cho c\u00f4ng ty MM2 khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/thiet-ke-thi-cong-nha-tai-da-nang\"><strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng<\/strong><\/a><\/span> nh\u00e9. MM2 lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia s\u1ebb gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft trong kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3 g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>B\u1ed3n t\u1eafm.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng v\u00f2i sen v\u00e0 v\u00f2i x\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<li>G\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ed3n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t (n\u1ebfu th\u00edch).<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1 treo qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o.<\/li>\n<li>B\u00ecnh n\u00f3ng l\u1ea1nh.<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ec7 x\u00ed t\u1ef1 ho\u1ea1i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm n\u00e0y c\u00f2n t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 t\u1eafm c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch 6m2 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp c\u00e1c v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch g\u1ecdn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh v\u01b0\u1edbng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm lu\u00f4n \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt, th\u1ea5m n\u01b0\u1edbc&#8230; n\u00ean khi mua \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n mua ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 b\u1ed3n. N\u00f3 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba b\u1ec1n theo th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed3 nh\u1ef1a, \u0111\u1ed3 inox&#8230; \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh r\u1ec9 s\u00e9t.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd n\u1eefa \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u1ea1ch l\u00e1t n\u1ec1n ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i g\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng, ch\u1ed1ng tr\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1ee7 \u00f3ng \u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00eam s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng cho ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm c\u0169ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 cho ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 6m2.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Tham kh\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1507\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/khong-gian-phong-tam.jpg\" alt=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 xinh\" width=\"600\" height=\"380\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1508\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/phong-tam-6-m2-dep-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 xinh\" width=\"530\" height=\"477\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1509\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/phong-tam-6-m2-dep-2.jpg\" alt=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm 6m2 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 xinh\" width=\"600\" height=\"462\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Hi v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cho b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng!<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean xem ngay: <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/thiet-ke-thi-cong-noi-that-da-nang\">C\u00f4ng ty thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p<\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 1 c\u0103n nh\u00e0 ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh. C\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c gia ch\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, ti\u1ec7n nghi&#8230; \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1506,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1505"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1505"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1505\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1510,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1505\/revisions\/1510"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1506"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1505"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1505"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1505"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp